<h3>Installing Robodoc</h3>
<p>If you pass the requirements above, you can install Robodoc simply by downloading it (via http[s] or git) to the webserver folder (for instance, <code class="inline">/var/www</code>):</p>
<code>git clone https://github.com/pulsir/robodoc.git</code>
<p>When that's done, visit the place you installed Robodoc to in your browser (for instance, <code class="inline">http://localhost/robodoc</code> or <code class="inline">http://dev.pulsir.eu/common/documentation/robodoc</code>). If the Robodoc site appears, you've succesfully installed Robodoc. If not, <a href="http://reddit.com/r/robodoc">try asking in our subreddit</a>.</p>
